rofit organization privacy policy about wikipedia disclaimers contact wikipedia developers cookie statement mobile view ruth porat  wikipedia ruth porat from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search ruth porat born  sale greater manchester england united kingdom nationality american alma mater stanford university london school of economics wharton school of the university of pennsylvania employer alphabet inc title chief financial officer spouses anthony paduano children  ruth porat born  is a britishborn american financial executive who is the current chief financial officer of alphabet inc of which google is a subsidiary as of may  she was the cfo and executive vice president of morgan stanley from january  to may  contents  early life and education  career  morgan stanley  google  boardships  political views  personal life  references early life and educationedit porat was born to a jewish family in sale greater manchester england the daughter of dr dan and frieda porat she moved at a young age to cambridge massachusetts where her father was a research fellow in the physics department at harvard university her father later relocated the family to palo alto california where he worked at the slac national accelerator laboratory for  years porat has a bachelor of arts degree in economics  international relations from stanford university and holds a master of science degree in industrial relations from london school of economics and an mba with distinction from wharton school of the university of pennsylvania careeredit morgan stanleyedit porat started her career at morgan stanley in  but left to follow morgan stanley president robert f greenhill to smith barney in  and returned to morgan stanley in  before becoming cfo she served as vice chairman of investment banking from september  to december  and global head of the financial institutions group from september  through december  she was previously the cohead of technology investment banking and worked for morgan stanley in london she is credited with creating the european debt financing that saved amazon from collapse during the dotcom melt down in  her financial partner during the internet investment banking craze was mary meeker who is the godmother to porats three children during the financial crisis porat led the morgan stanley team advising the united states department of the treasury regarding fannie mae and freddie mac and the new york federal reserve bank with respect to aig in the  hbo movie too big to fail porat is played by jennifer van dyck in may  she presented to the bretton woods committee hosted by the international monetary fund in washington dc on postcrisis reform and financial legislation and to the world economic forum in davos in  on trust levels within and of the financial sector in  it was reported that president barack obama would nominate porat as the next deputy secretary of the treasury however it was reported later by bloomberg news and the new york times that porat had contacted white house officials to withdraw her name from consideration because of improving conditions at morgan stanley and the acrimonious confirmation process inflicted upon then treasury secretarynominee jack lew porats career was analyzed in the mckinsey  company study how remarkable women lead she was named best financial institutions cfo in a poll conducted by institutional investor for its  allamerica executive team googleedit on march   it was announced that porat would join google as their new cfo as of may   bloomberg business reported that her hiring deal included financial incentives that will eventually amount to  million by  she has been credited with boosting googles share price by reorganizing the company and imposing financial discipline for the first time boardshipsedit she is a vice chair of the board of trustees of stanford university a member of the board of directors of stanford management company the borrowing advisory committee of the united states treasury the board of directors of the council on foreign relations the board of trustees of the economic club of new york and the bretton woods committee she is a member of the advisory council of the hutchins center on fiscal and monetary policy at the brookings institution political viewsedit porat supported senator hillary clinton when she ran for president in  hosting a fundraiser at her apartment in the dakota in new york city in  porat expressed her support for increased taxes on the wealthy and declared on the topic of significant spending decreases that we cannot cut our way to greatness personal lifeedit porat has been married to anthony paduano partner in the law firm of paduano  weintraub since  porat is a survivor of breast cancer referencesedit  a b mcgrath maggie march   google lures cfo ruth porat from morgan stanley forbes   patricia garcia ruth porat is googles first female cfo  other powerful women in tech vogue retrieved    a b worlds most powerful women ruth porat forbes august    shamah david  new google cfo ruth porats family a mirror of american jewry the times of israel retrieved    a b c ruth porat council on foreign relations   a b ruth porat wed to law student the new york times december     dr frieda porats obituary  a dossier on morgan stanleys new cfo ruth porat the wall street journal december     ruth porat to join google as chief financial officer alphabet march     a b craig suzanne november   dealbook a female wall st financial chief avoids pitfalls that stymied others the new york times   the everything store jeff bezos and the age of amazon little brown  co p  new york  templatevoxthe littleknown deal that saved amazon from the dotcom crash timothy b lee april    sorkin andrew ross  too big to fail viking press pp   isbn    when treasury calls the deal september    too big to fail on imdb   bretton woods annual meeting risks to the global system the bretton woods committee may     edelman trust barometer edelman janua