e economic club of new york and the bretton woods committee she is a member of the advisory council of the hutchins center on fiscal and monetary policy at the brookings institution political viewsedit porat supported senator hillary clinton when she ran for president in  hosting a fundraiser at her apartment in the dakota in new york city in  porat expressed her support for increased taxes on the wealthy and declared on the topic of significant spending decreases that we cannot cut our way to greatness personal lifeedit porat has been married to anthony paduano partner in the law firm of paduano  weintraub since  porat is a survivor of breast cancer referencesedit  a b mcgrath maggie march   google lures cfo ruth porat from morgan stanley forbes   patricia garcia ruth porat is googles first female cfo  other powerful women in tech vogue retrieved    a b worlds most powerful women ruth porat forbes august    shamah david  new google cfo ruth porats family a mirror of american jewry the times of israel retrieved    a b c ruth porat council on foreign relations   a b ruth porat wed to law student the new york times december     dr frieda porats obituary  a dossier on morgan stanleys new cfo ruth porat the wall street journal december     ruth porat to join google as chief financial officer alphabet march     a b craig suzanne november   dealbook a female wall st financial chief avoids pitfalls that stymied others the new york times   the everything store jeff bezos and the age of amazon little brown  co p  new york  templatevoxthe littleknown deal that saved amazon from the dotcom crash timothy b lee april    sorkin andrew ross  too big to fail viking press pp   isbn    when treasury calls the deal september    too big to fail on imdb   bretton woods annual meeting risks to the global system the bretton woods committee may     edelman trust barometer edelman january    ruth porat world economic forum december    obama considering morgan stanleys porat for treasury job